Description: The IndivSTATIS package provides code for IndivSTATIS: a multivariate methods to analyze multiple connectivity matrices derived from individualized parcellation. IndivSTATIS accommodates for unequal sizes of parcels/networks across individuals (for example, those derived from Gordon et al.'s arrpoach.)
